v1.0
    initial release
    Huawei E3372h (NCM mode, USB PID 12d1:1506) support for Venus OS
    D-Bus modem service (com.victronenergy.modem) with signal, network, IMEI
    NCM data connection via AT^NDISDUP + DHCP on wwan0
    udev rules for serial-starter and hotplug
    configurable APN via /data/e3372-config.conf
